Botswana Diamonds has announced the acquisition of an additional stake in the prospective Maibwe joint venture in Botswana. Chairman, John Teeling commented: “We are delighted that after several years of negotiating with the liquidators of BCL Botswana which held in its portfolio the Maibwe diamond joint venture in the Kalahari of Botswana that we have been able to unlock the corporate logjam and are now able to move ahead to examine properly the true potential of the Maibwe concession”.